WEBVTT

00:17.160 --> 00:18.020
This is poison.

00:19.030 --> 00:20.230
I had someone test it.

00:21.230 --> 00:23.290
It won't take effect until tomorrow.

00:23.620 --> 00:24.890
It will be painless.

00:26.190 --> 00:27.550
To die tomorrow?

00:29.350 --> 00:30.320
What's the use

00:31.600 --> 00:32.750
of keeping me alive

00:34.280 --> 00:35.750
until tomorrow?

00:39.840 --> 00:42.170
Xiao Wuyi has agreed to cooperate with me.

00:42.670 --> 00:43.750
But now,

00:44.880 --> 00:46.740
there's still one thing missing—

00:47.000 --> 00:48.330
a pledge of allegiance.

00:52.840 --> 00:54.200
So you want to use my life

00:55.150 --> 00:57.080
to announce Xiao Wuyi's betrayal.

01:06.840 --> 01:07.480
Lejun!

01:08.590 --> 01:09.740
Have you lost your mind?

01:09.740 --> 01:10.760
This is a deadly poison!

01:10.760 --> 01:12.760
Wasn't it you who told me to drink it?

01:12.950 --> 01:13.590
But

01:14.310 --> 01:15.570
I could have found a way

01:15.870 --> 01:16.870
to keep you alive.

01:17.240 --> 01:18.700
Didn't it ever occur to you

01:19.070 --> 01:20.150
to beg me just once?

01:30.789 --> 01:32.320
But I no longer wish to live.

01:34.680 --> 01:35.509
Mulian Yu.

01:37.509 --> 01:40.680
What are you still pretending for?

01:42.000 --> 01:43.920
Did you bring poison here today

01:44.759 --> 01:46.400
just to hear me beg for mercy?

01:48.509 --> 01:49.479
Three years.

01:50.840 --> 01:53.039
You've been by my side for 3 years.

01:53.560 --> 01:55.390
Three years of marriage between us—

01:55.390 --> 01:56.570
all my indulgence toward you,

01:56.570 --> 01:58.280
all the affection I showed you—

01:58.280 --> 02:01.480
did none of it earn
even a shred of your genuine affection?

02:05.150 --> 02:06.040
No.

02:08.910 --> 02:10.440
Our homelands are enemies.

02:10.840 --> 02:12.190
All my blood relatives

02:12.190 --> 02:14.520
were killed by you Northern Qin people.

02:16.150 --> 02:18.680
Our families have been sworn enemies
for generations.

02:18.680 --> 02:21.610
How could there be any genuine affection
between us?

02:38.710 --> 02:39.680
Mulian Yu.

02:41.960 --> 02:44.310
Can you promise me one thing?

02:47.630 --> 02:50.280
If one day you win

02:51.030 --> 02:54.030
and lead your army to attack Jiankang,

02:55.710 --> 02:58.470
can you please

02:59.030 --> 03:00.430
spare my brother's life?

03:01.400 --> 03:03.120
He's the only family

03:03.680 --> 03:05.280
I have left in this world.

03:08.590 --> 03:09.320
Ridiculous.

03:11.080 --> 03:12.480
Absolutely ridiculous.

03:17.280 --> 03:18.590
If Heaven favors me

03:19.750 --> 03:21.150
and that day truly comes.

03:22.310 --> 03:24.040
I'll kill him with my own hands.

03:27.240 --> 03:29.500
That way, you two can be reunited sooner,

03:30.120 --> 03:33.470
and it won't have been in vain
that you submitted yourself to the enemy,

03:33.470 --> 03:35.980
exhausting your wits

03:37.000 --> 03:39.400
and plotting your entire life
for his sake.

03:43.560 --> 03:44.590
Mulian Yu!

03:50.630 --> 03:51.680
I'm sorry.

04:02.910 --> 04:04.080
Sorry that

04:05.590 --> 04:07.650
I've schemed against you once again.

04:08.590 --> 04:09.850
If there is a next life,

04:10.590 --> 04:13.150
may we meet again
with different identities.

06:18.620 --> 06:23.000
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

06:23.080 --> 06:25.910
[Episode 27]

06:27.070 --> 06:28.390
Xiao Wuyi!

06:40.159 --> 06:41.830
If you truly have faith in him,

06:43.240 --> 06:44.480
please allow him

06:45.560 --> 06:48.680
to stand before you as a true rival.

07:25.800 --> 07:26.270
Lejun.

07:27.240 --> 07:27.720
Lejun!

07:29.670 --> 07:34.810
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

07:33.159 --> 07:33.720
Lejun!

07:35.740 --> 07:41.320
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

07:35.800 --> 07:36.310
Lejun.

07:37.070 --> 07:37.870
Mao.

07:38.120 --> 07:39.040
I came too late.

07:40.000 --> 07:43.920
You finally came to pick me up.

07:41.980 --> 07:48.280
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

07:45.040 --> 07:45.560
Lejun.

07:48.390 --> 07:51.270
I... I want to go home.

07:48.550 --> 07:55.030
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

07:52.270 --> 07:54.360
Lejun... Lejun...

07:55.540 --> 08:00.960
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong? ♪

07:55.920 --> 07:56.430
Go...

08:01.560 --> 08:06.930
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

08:07.730 --> 08:11.380
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

08:11.480 --> 08:13.930
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

08:12.950 --> 08:13.680
Lejun!

08:14.160 --> 08:20.180
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

08:18.000 --> 08:20.870
Xiao Wuyi!

08:20.450 --> 08:24.010
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

08:22.870 --> 08:25.310
Mao, I'm so tired.

08:24.030 --> 08:27.000
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

08:25.800 --> 08:27.070
The Eagle King has treated me very well.

08:27.030 --> 08:32.500
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

08:27.720 --> 08:29.520
He knew all along that I was a spy,

08:29.560 --> 08:32.630
yet he still sincerely wanted to give me
a peaceful life for the years I had left.

08:32.630 --> 08:35.030
But I could never give him
my genuine affection.

08:35.030 --> 08:37.270
With the deep-seated hatred
between our Prince Qi's household and him,

08:37.270 --> 08:39.240
I could neither love him nor hate him.

08:39.240 --> 08:40.840
Once our two nations go to war,

08:40.840 --> 08:43.360
it's bound to be a fight
where one side must die.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.960
Today, I'm returning those 3 stolen years

08:44.960 --> 08:46.790
to Jiayu all at once.

08:47.480 --> 08:48.360
With my death,

08:48.790 --> 08:50.240
Xiao Wuyi should be able to gain

08:50.240 --> 08:51.630
the trust of Northern Qin.

08:51.630 --> 08:52.870
Perhaps this can finally atone

08:52.870 --> 08:55.000
for the sins I committed at Lingfeng Fort.

08:55.000 --> 08:56.910
Please allow me to use this life of mine

08:56.910 --> 08:58.550
to finally usher in the beginning of

08:58.550 --> 09:00.080
your imperial legacy, Mao.

09:01.000 --> 09:01.600
Mao.

09:02.030 --> 09:02.790
Forgive me.

09:03.360 --> 09:04.440
I want to rest now.

09:06.630 --> 09:07.440
Retreat!

09:20.790 --> 09:23.480
What if I don't want
to be the wife of the infamous Demon Xiao,

09:23.480 --> 09:24.840
but the wife of a hero?

09:25.800 --> 09:28.580
I want you to live a long life,

09:28.880 --> 09:29.920
to live in peace,

09:30.750 --> 09:32.630
to leave behind an honorable name,

09:32.630 --> 09:34.160
and to be remembered by all.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.670
You are making things difficult for me.

09:36.670 --> 09:37.470
That's right.

09:37.910 --> 09:39.040
I insist on doing so.

09:39.720 --> 09:40.920
Will you listen to me?

10:05.470 --> 10:08.890
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

10:09.200 --> 10:12.810
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

10:12.870 --> 10:13.790
On the day of the competition,

10:12.980 --> 10:17.340
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

10:13.910 --> 10:15.110
I took a liking to you.

10:16.200 --> 10:17.700
My desire to marry you
comes from my heart.

10:17.700 --> 10:20.400
♪ So desolate ♪

10:18.390 --> 10:19.450
It was never an act.

10:20.360 --> 10:21.080
It's no coincidence.

10:20.980 --> 10:24.650
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

10:22.360 --> 10:24.420
I came here specifically to find you.

10:24.670 --> 10:28.210
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

10:25.000 --> 10:26.760
With such a beauty
throwing herself into my arms,

10:26.760 --> 10:28.360
how could I possibly refuse?

10:28.400 --> 10:33.730
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

10:34.230 --> 10:37.050
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

10:37.080 --> 10:39.570
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

10:39.830 --> 10:44.000
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

10:44.020 --> 10:47.620
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

10:47.870 --> 10:49.640
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

10:49.870 --> 10:52.490
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

10:52.520 --> 10:55.180
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

10:55.360 --> 10:59.600
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

10:59.630 --> 11:04.470
♪ I just want to see you one more time ♪

11:12.200 --> 11:13.800
I've brought your two guards

11:13.910 --> 11:14.870
back to you.

11:16.630 --> 11:18.270
Aren't you worried I'll run away?

11:18.270 --> 11:19.000
Yesterday,

11:19.480 --> 11:20.940
in front of the two armies,

11:21.150 --> 11:23.410
you killed Li Lejun in front of everyone,

11:23.440 --> 11:25.100
proving your determination.

11:25.840 --> 11:27.440
With this pledge of loyalty,

11:27.630 --> 11:29.830
what more could I possibly worry about?

11:31.910 --> 11:32.550
What?

11:34.270 --> 11:35.330
You want to kill me?

11:37.240 --> 11:38.030
Xiao Wuyi.

11:38.250 --> 11:40.510
You've actually chosen to side with
the Northern Qin bandits.

11:40.510 --> 11:42.110
Are you still worthy of the title of
Crown Prince Wenxi?

11:42.110 --> 11:43.550
How can you face the brothers
of the Beifu Army?

11:43.550 --> 11:45.750
I, Xiao Wuyi, have never feared
what others say.

11:45.750 --> 11:46.840
If I hadn't done this,

11:46.840 --> 11:47.510
would you

11:47.680 --> 11:49.410
and those people of Southern Ye
trapped in that sheep pen

11:49.410 --> 11:51.140
still have a chance to survive?

11:51.630 --> 11:53.630
Li Mao slaughtered my entire family

11:53.720 --> 11:55.790
and seized control of the Beifu Army
from me.

11:55.790 --> 11:57.670
Now, driven by greed for glory,
he's rushing headlong into danger,

11:57.670 --> 11:59.530
poised to send our Beifu soldiers

11:59.630 --> 12:01.750
straight under the blades and axes
of the Northern Qin Army.

12:01.750 --> 12:03.790
When that happens, forget about
the Northern Expedition—

12:03.790 --> 12:06.030
even the entire Northern Border will fall.

12:06.030 --> 12:07.630
Soon enough, you'll find out

12:07.870 --> 12:10.320
who's right and who's wrong.

12:11.510 --> 12:12.970
My deal with the Eagle King

12:13.840 --> 12:14.790
is nothing more than a way to reclaim

12:14.790 --> 12:16.590
what originally belonged to me.

12:19.000 --> 12:21.630
Whether to stay... Or to leave,

12:23.150 --> 12:24.420
it's up to you.

12:26.600 --> 12:29.390
My parents were both killed
by the people of Northern Qin.

12:29.390 --> 12:31.840
I swear I'll never ally myself with
these bandits in this lifetime.

12:31.840 --> 12:32.670
Xiao Wuyi,

12:33.960 --> 12:36.890
you're not worthy of the title
of Crown Prince Wenxi.

12:41.480 --> 12:43.410
Please forgive us, Your Highness.

12:52.240 --> 12:53.640
Whether they live or die,

12:54.270 --> 12:56.440
Young Lord Xiao, it's your call.

12:56.840 --> 12:58.550
They're just 2 stray dogs.

12:59.510 --> 13:00.840
Let them get lost.

13:07.320 --> 13:08.250
Don't look back.

13:08.630 --> 13:10.560
The more isolated His Highness is,

13:10.600 --> 13:12.730
the more the Eagle King will trust him.

13:29.120 --> 13:30.980
Lejun wanted to completely sever

13:31.270 --> 13:33.200
the bond between you and Xiao Wuyi.

13:36.200 --> 13:37.800
Just like how it was back then

13:38.120 --> 13:39.450
with my mother's death.

13:41.440 --> 13:43.700
No matter how many reasons I came up with,

13:44.270 --> 13:45.320
or how many excuses I made for Lejun

13:45.320 --> 13:46.390
in my heart,

13:46.960 --> 13:48.420
the friendship between us

13:49.540 --> 13:51.070
still came to an abrupt end.

13:55.150 --> 13:56.030
Because

13:58.270 --> 13:59.800
that was my dearest mother.

14:01.360 --> 14:02.030
She always hoped

14:02.030 --> 14:03.690
I could become a true emperor,

14:06.120 --> 14:07.980
free from anyone's constraints.

14:10.150 --> 14:13.150
She was worried I'd become too dependent
on Xiao Wuyi,

14:14.240 --> 14:15.290
and that

14:18.720 --> 14:20.720
I'd let my guard down because of you.

14:24.200 --> 14:25.800
Through this deadly gambit,

14:26.910 --> 14:29.440
she fulfilled the plan
Wuyi and I had devised,

14:31.200 --> 14:32.390
yet she also severed all ties

14:32.390 --> 14:33.920
between us once and for all.

14:46.840 --> 14:49.440
"Five days from now,
when the north wind rises,

14:50.030 --> 14:51.430
meet at Dingfeng Slope."

14:52.000 --> 14:54.460
This was found on the sole of
Li Lejun's shoe.

15:07.240 --> 15:09.440
It seems the day for the decisive battle

15:10.870 --> 15:11.870
has finally come.

15:12.180 --> 15:14.110
The new caltrop fireball is ready.

15:14.510 --> 15:16.750
It's completely different from
the previous version.

15:16.750 --> 15:18.010
I'll take you to see it.

15:50.560 --> 15:51.270
I'll go make the record.

15:51.270 --> 15:51.820
Okay.

15:57.550 --> 15:58.720
This is called "stone fat,"

15:58.720 --> 16:00.000
also known as "weishui."

16:00.000 --> 16:02.320
Stone fat oil deposits
are different from lard or tallow.

16:02.320 --> 16:04.030
They form alongside mineral deposits.

16:04.030 --> 16:05.890
They are flammable but inedible,

16:06.080 --> 16:07.670
and even water cannot extinguish them.

16:07.670 --> 16:08.870
They can stretch for thousands of miles

16:08.870 --> 16:10.070
and burn without end.

16:12.550 --> 16:14.480
Even water can't extinguish them?

16:14.840 --> 16:15.790
Then with this substance,

16:15.790 --> 16:17.390
we'll surely be invincible.

16:22.000 --> 16:23.240
I once promised Wuyi

16:23.630 --> 16:27.150
that I'd create the caltrop fireball
before the Northern Expedition.

16:27.150 --> 16:29.630
Though he's not here today
and cannot see it,

16:30.870 --> 16:32.600
I haven't failed in my mission.

16:37.790 --> 16:38.650
I have to go now.

16:40.870 --> 16:41.800
But don't worry.

16:42.550 --> 16:46.280
Cui Shao'an is overseeing
the production of the caltrop fireball.

16:46.790 --> 16:48.250
Are you going to find Wuyi?

16:52.120 --> 16:53.640
This battle could result in
a great victory

16:53.640 --> 16:55.470
for the Beifu Army,

16:56.390 --> 16:57.670
for Ye, and for you.

16:58.550 --> 16:59.960
But for Xiao Wuyi,

17:01.310 --> 17:02.430
defeat is certain.

17:05.030 --> 17:06.910
He had already resolved to die,

17:07.589 --> 17:09.920
and now, the two-month deadline
is nearly up,

17:09.920 --> 17:12.200
and the miraculous doctor's medicine
won't last much longer.

17:12.200 --> 17:13.260
I won't let him die.

17:13.920 --> 17:15.119
I'm going to find him.

17:15.720 --> 17:17.849
I'll definitely bring him back alive.

17:19.550 --> 17:22.270
The loyalty to stand through
life and death together—

17:22.270 --> 17:23.800
that's the Xie Jiayu I know.

17:25.880 --> 17:26.400
Go on.

17:27.680 --> 17:28.790
You're not stopping me?

17:28.790 --> 17:29.440
I tried.

17:31.720 --> 17:32.580
But I couldn't.

17:35.590 --> 17:36.190
Take care.

17:37.330 --> 17:38.330
You take care too.

17:46.440 --> 17:49.040
Do you really have to go to
the Northern Border?

17:49.680 --> 17:51.680
I built the Beifu Army all by myself,

17:52.310 --> 17:54.640
and they once answered only to my command.

17:55.030 --> 17:59.000
Three years have passed since the reforms.
The military system may have changed,

17:59.000 --> 18:01.030
but the loyalty of the soldiers has not.

18:01.030 --> 18:01.680
Yizhi.

18:02.510 --> 18:05.640
The tragedy of the An and Lu families
must never happen again.

18:05.640 --> 18:07.070
The army's loyalty should not
lie with one man,

18:07.070 --> 18:08.200
but with the people.

18:09.480 --> 18:10.640
No matter who becomes the commander of

18:10.640 --> 18:11.500
the Beifu Army,

18:11.880 --> 18:13.510
and even without me, Xiao Wuyi,

18:13.510 --> 18:14.840
the Beifu Army must know

18:15.590 --> 18:17.250
that they are fighting for Ye.

18:17.920 --> 18:19.580
So you don't plan to come back?

18:23.310 --> 18:25.170
Will we ever see each other again?

18:38.110 --> 18:40.310
I hope that, in the final days of my life,

18:40.350 --> 18:42.950
I can pave the way for
the Northern Expedition.

18:44.590 --> 18:46.990
Was this your plan
from the very beginning?

18:48.440 --> 18:49.900
What about Xie Jiayu then?

18:51.680 --> 18:52.810
Tell Xiao Wuyi that,

18:53.550 --> 18:54.350
as he wished,

18:55.590 --> 18:58.650
the next time we meet,
it will be as emperor and subject.

19:01.240 --> 19:02.480
Got it, Mao.

19:03.510 --> 19:05.350
Goodbye, Yaoyao.

19:12.480 --> 19:13.880
Your Highness Prince Qi,

19:15.110 --> 19:16.370
I hereby take my leave.

19:27.240 --> 19:27.960
Goodbye,

19:30.110 --> 19:30.790
Xie Jiayu.

19:32.230 --> 19:35.650
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

19:35.960 --> 19:39.630
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

19:39.740 --> 19:44.110
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

19:40.580 --> 19:43.440
Bring all the military reports
and memorials here.

19:44.470 --> 19:47.160
♪ So desolate ♪

19:47.740 --> 19:51.410
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

19:51.430 --> 19:54.970
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

19:55.160 --> 20:00.440
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

20:00.480 --> 20:01.550
I won't get married.

20:01.140 --> 20:04.580
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

20:02.420 --> 20:04.420
I just want to stay by your side, Mao.

20:04.600 --> 20:08.600
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

20:05.920 --> 20:08.650
I have the best older brother
in the entire world.

20:08.730 --> 20:12.440
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

20:10.720 --> 20:11.350
Mao.

20:12.470 --> 20:15.760
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

20:13.160 --> 20:15.090
I will protect you, no matter what.

20:16.080 --> 20:18.900
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

20:18.930 --> 20:21.420
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

20:22.060 --> 20:26.300
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

20:26.630 --> 20:30.800
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

20:30.990 --> 20:34.970
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

20:43.110 --> 20:45.170
We've just received a battle report.

20:46.750 --> 20:49.030
Last night, scouts detected a sudden fire

20:49.030 --> 20:51.030
breaking out at the Beifu Army Camp.

20:51.240 --> 20:53.300
Li Mao's army immediately broke camp

20:53.680 --> 20:55.750
and marched westward,
bypassing the Jing River.

20:55.750 --> 20:57.410
He's going to Dingfeng Slope.

20:58.480 --> 20:59.410
Dingfeng Slope?

21:00.110 --> 21:01.710
Li Mao must be heading there,

21:01.920 --> 21:06.030
because Dingfeng Slope holds a secret
that has never been revealed to outsiders.

21:06.030 --> 21:06.920
What secret?

21:08.070 --> 21:09.560
To the south of Dingfeng Slope

21:09.560 --> 21:11.830
are 2 iron mines marked by
the Phoenix Heart Tokens.

21:11.830 --> 21:13.290
If he holds Dingfeng Slope

21:13.720 --> 21:16.030
and establishes
a Directorate of Military Equipment there,

21:16.030 --> 21:17.030
using it as a base

21:17.720 --> 21:18.960
to train troops, forge weapons,

21:18.960 --> 21:20.480
store grain, and raise livestock,

21:20.480 --> 21:22.400
not only will the capture of the Capital
be just a matter of time,

21:22.400 --> 21:25.830
but he'll also no longer have to rely on
the aristocratic clans for supplies.

21:25.830 --> 21:26.690
Your Highness.

21:27.920 --> 21:29.250
There's a woman outside

21:29.480 --> 21:31.480
claiming to be Xiao Wuyi's consort.

21:37.200 --> 21:38.440
Let me go.

21:40.350 --> 21:41.590
I just told you,

21:41.590 --> 21:42.990
I am Xiao Wuyi's consort.

21:43.680 --> 21:44.640
If you don't believe me,

21:44.640 --> 21:46.770
just call him out and ask him yourself.

21:47.110 --> 21:48.240
Xiao Wuyi, I'm here!

21:48.590 --> 21:49.320
Xiao Wuyi...

21:49.680 --> 21:50.350
Look at him.

21:50.440 --> 21:51.350
Just let me go.

21:52.110 --> 21:53.640
You... Tell him to let me go.

21:54.590 --> 21:55.190
Xiao Wuyi.

21:55.550 --> 21:56.680
What are you doing here?

21:56.680 --> 21:58.440
I'm here to share life and death with you.

21:58.440 --> 21:59.040
Xiao Wuyi.

21:59.510 --> 22:00.920
I had to set the Beifu Army Camp

22:00.920 --> 22:02.400
on fire just to escape.

22:02.790 --> 22:04.070
And this is how you greet me?

22:04.070 --> 22:07.270
All those days I spent crying for you
were for nothing then.

22:07.270 --> 22:09.640
Xie Jiayu, long time no see.

22:10.310 --> 22:11.240
It seems you are truly devoted

22:11.240 --> 22:12.680
to Young Lord Xiao.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.270
Let her in.

22:19.510 --> 22:20.070
Yes!

22:25.480 --> 22:27.280
The food is ready. Please enjoy.

22:37.590 --> 22:38.320
Xiao Wuyi...

22:56.270 --> 22:58.600
Now that you've escaped Li Mao's control,

22:58.830 --> 23:00.400
you could go anywhere you wish.

23:00.400 --> 23:02.400
Why come running here
and throw yourself into danger?

23:02.400 --> 23:03.270
Are you crazy?

23:09.030 --> 23:09.830
Don't you know

23:10.110 --> 23:11.480
that once you enter this place,

23:11.480 --> 23:13.480
leaving will be nearly impossible?

23:14.270 --> 23:16.200
How many times do I have to tell you?

23:17.070 --> 23:19.330
I'm here to share life and death
with you.

23:20.270 --> 23:21.000
Understood?

23:25.480 --> 23:26.160
But

23:26.720 --> 23:29.200
if you're bothered by the fact
that Li Mao forced me to marry him,

23:29.200 --> 23:30.660
then I'll leave right now.

23:31.440 --> 23:33.500
What nonsense are you talking about?

23:34.480 --> 23:36.880
Then why haven't you smiled at me
even once?

23:40.960 --> 23:42.620
I've already resolved to die.

23:45.550 --> 23:47.680
My reputation out there is in tatters.

23:47.720 --> 23:49.120
Why should I drag you down

23:49.480 --> 23:50.810
to suffer alongside me?

23:51.000 --> 23:53.330
Didn't we promise each other long ago that

23:53.880 --> 23:55.810
whether you achieve glory and fame

23:56.270 --> 23:57.870
or are reviled by the masses,

23:58.350 --> 23:59.950
I will always be by your side?

24:00.790 --> 24:02.450
I, Xie Jiayu, stand by my word.

24:05.270 --> 24:06.070
Xiao Wuyi.

24:07.270 --> 24:10.070
As husband and wife,
our fates are bound together.

24:10.350 --> 24:11.880
All I want is for you to live.

24:21.240 --> 24:22.900
Even if everyone abandons me,

24:23.830 --> 24:25.360
as long as you're by my side,

24:26.350 --> 24:29.010
I, Xiao Wuyi, won't have lived this life
in vain.

24:30.270 --> 24:32.130
Once I've wiped out Li Mao's army,

24:33.920 --> 24:34.980
I'll come find you.

24:37.750 --> 24:39.400
The weapon I promised you—

24:40.070 --> 24:41.600
I've successfully made it.

24:55.750 --> 24:56.610
Your Highness.

24:57.640 --> 24:58.960
Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

24:59.030 --> 25:00.560
have been doing nothing but

25:00.640 --> 25:01.960
eating and drinking all day.

25:01.960 --> 25:03.400
What do you make of this, Imperial Envoy

25:03.400 --> 25:04.860
Do you think Young Lord Xiao's consort

25:04.860 --> 25:06.420
really just came here

25:06.920 --> 25:08.620
to share life and death with Xiao Wuyi?

25:08.620 --> 25:10.750
I've heard a saying among common folk,

25:10.920 --> 25:12.920
"Husband and wife are like
birds of a feather.

25:12.920 --> 25:15.110
But when disaster strikes,
they fly their separate ways."

25:15.110 --> 25:16.750
Your Highness surely
doesn't really believe

25:16.750 --> 25:19.750
there's anyone in this world
who'd die for love, do you?

25:19.750 --> 25:21.410
I certainly don't believe it.

25:21.830 --> 25:23.960
But that Xie Jiayu is truly different.

25:24.680 --> 25:25.720
Back in Jiankang,

25:26.000 --> 25:28.060
Xiao Wuyi was deeply in love with her,

25:28.200 --> 25:30.110
yet she was childhood sweethearts
with Li Mao.

25:30.110 --> 25:31.710
Between Xiao Wuyi and Li Mao,

25:32.550 --> 25:34.950
Li Lejun's death was merely
the last straw.

25:35.440 --> 25:37.680
The one who truly drove those two apart

25:38.270 --> 25:39.270
was Xie Jiayu.

25:39.640 --> 25:41.160
Since Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

25:41.160 --> 25:42.420
share such a deep bond,

25:42.920 --> 25:44.920
doesn't that mean we've got

25:44.920 --> 25:46.460
even more leverage against Xiao Wuyi now?

25:46.460 --> 25:47.660
His Majesty means...

25:50.920 --> 25:53.310
This is a rare opportunity.

25:55.590 --> 25:57.680
Very well. As His Majesty commands,

25:58.400 --> 26:00.270
even if the mines at Dingfeng Slope

26:00.270 --> 26:01.930
turn out to be a colossal trap,

26:02.310 --> 26:03.880
we shall still brave it.

26:04.310 --> 26:05.980
Beat the drums and muster the troops!

26:05.980 --> 26:06.710
Understood!

26:16.480 --> 26:18.940
Your Highness, please don't go
any further.

26:21.830 --> 26:22.540
Got it.

26:23.290 --> 26:24.620
You all head back first.

26:26.830 --> 26:27.350
What?

26:27.880 --> 26:29.880
Are Heir's words
no longer enough to command you?

26:29.880 --> 26:30.880
His Highness said

26:31.110 --> 26:32.790
that Heir's an important guest here,

26:32.790 --> 26:34.270
yet you keep watching us every day.

26:34.270 --> 26:37.470
Do you intend to eavesdrop
on our private affairs as well?

26:38.830 --> 26:39.440
Step back.

26:57.400 --> 26:58.310
The Eagle King probably thought

26:58.310 --> 27:00.030
you came here to gather information.

27:00.030 --> 27:01.290
Who would have thought

27:01.680 --> 27:03.610
you really came to join me in death?

27:04.310 --> 27:05.400
So, are you saying

27:05.400 --> 27:06.660
I shouldn't have come?

27:11.350 --> 27:12.410
I didn't mean that.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.590
Tell me the truth—

27:14.590 --> 27:16.350
were you happy to see me?

27:19.830 --> 27:20.350
I was.

27:22.830 --> 27:23.630
I was so happy.

27:25.920 --> 27:27.580
Then do you know how upset I was

27:27.590 --> 27:28.850
when I saw your letter?

27:31.750 --> 27:34.000
Xiao Wuyi, if you ever do
something like this again,

27:34.000 --> 27:35.900
I will absolutely not forgive you.

27:35.900 --> 27:36.620
Or

27:36.650 --> 27:38.380
you can just go live with Li Mao.

27:40.680 --> 27:42.960
No, that's not right either. Li Mao said

27:44.640 --> 27:45.840
the next time you met,

27:46.480 --> 27:47.350
as you wished,

27:47.640 --> 27:49.370
it'd be as emperor and subject.

27:52.440 --> 27:54.000
The coroner has done the autopsy.

27:54.000 --> 27:55.270
Before Lejun died,

27:55.270 --> 27:56.930
she had already taken poison.

27:57.540 --> 27:59.700
You never meant to shoot that arrow.

28:01.000 --> 28:02.800
Even if Li Lejun had taken poison

28:04.160 --> 28:05.490
and was destined to die,

28:06.960 --> 28:08.490
Lejun was still his sister.

28:09.830 --> 28:11.290
In the end, what that arrow

28:12.510 --> 28:14.030
shot through was the youthful friendship

28:14.030 --> 28:15.630
between Xiao Wuyi and Li Mao.

28:16.960 --> 28:18.360
Then on the battlefield,

28:19.270 --> 28:19.920
you two...

28:20.960 --> 28:22.110
No matter how my relationship with Yizhi

28:22.110 --> 28:23.030
changes,

28:24.270 --> 28:25.800
when it comes to Southern Ye

28:25.880 --> 28:27.480
and the affairs of the court,

28:27.590 --> 28:29.920
we'll always share the same aspirations.

28:31.750 --> 28:33.880
This is something he'll never change.

28:36.750 --> 28:39.010
Now that so many people have sacrificed,

28:39.550 --> 28:41.550
no matter how hard the road ahead is,

28:42.550 --> 28:44.950
we must persevere and keep moving forward.

28:45.790 --> 28:46.880
Did Lejun

28:48.200 --> 28:49.640
leave any final words?

28:55.590 --> 28:57.120
If you ever have the chance,

28:57.640 --> 29:00.100
please deliver this message to Jiayu
for me:

29:01.400 --> 29:02.860
I have never done anything

29:03.590 --> 29:05.110
in my life that I regret.

29:06.680 --> 29:08.210
Be it resentment or hatred,

29:08.920 --> 29:10.720
I've accepted it all willingly.

29:11.310 --> 29:13.040
As I reach the end of my journey,

29:13.350 --> 29:14.280
my only regret is

29:15.110 --> 29:16.790
that I won't be able to

29:18.400 --> 29:20.930
view the beautiful landscapes
of Ye with her.

29:24.790 --> 29:25.920
Why are you sighing?

29:28.590 --> 29:29.200
Nothing.

29:30.270 --> 29:32.400
I just hope when we return to Jiankang,

29:32.830 --> 29:35.960
we'll still make it in time for
the Thousand Lantern Festival.

29:35.960 --> 29:38.420
The journey of life is like
sailing on a boat.

29:39.950 --> 29:42.620
The passengers come and go,

29:44.110 --> 29:45.030
and some people

29:46.200 --> 29:48.720
are destined to accompany you
only for a part of the journey.

29:48.720 --> 29:51.480
When their time comes, they will leave.

29:54.790 --> 29:56.050
We must learn to let go.

29:57.240 --> 29:58.350
That may be true,

29:59.550 --> 30:00.240
but I don't want to hear

30:00.240 --> 30:01.440
any words of ill omen.

30:01.640 --> 30:02.400
Not today,

30:02.880 --> 30:03.720
not tomorrow.

30:06.070 --> 30:07.750
Xiao Wuyi, hold out your hand.

30:17.110 --> 30:17.840
What is this?

30:18.070 --> 30:19.530
This is a life-saving pill

30:19.750 --> 30:21.680
I begged the miraculous doctor to make.

30:21.680 --> 30:22.590
Keep it safe.

30:36.400 --> 30:38.000
Why are there so many people?

30:48.750 --> 30:49.610
Your Highness.

30:53.200 --> 30:54.440
What's this supposed to mean?

30:54.440 --> 30:55.640
Throughout history,

30:55.750 --> 30:56.960
whenever generals went off to war,

30:56.960 --> 30:59.070
their family members were often
held as hostages.

30:59.070 --> 31:01.640
Li Lejun took this poison as well.

31:04.480 --> 31:05.640
As long as we win,

31:06.240 --> 31:09.380
Young Lord Xiao, your consort
and the people of Southern Ye

31:09.380 --> 31:11.040
will surely be safe and sound.

31:30.920 --> 31:33.310
Your Highness, this place is surrounded by
mountains on all sides,

31:33.310 --> 31:35.600
with only a small road
leading out to the northeast.

31:35.600 --> 31:37.800
If the Beifu Army are to block this road,

31:37.960 --> 31:39.640
we'll be trapped here with no escape.

31:39.640 --> 31:41.440
Although this map is authentic,

31:41.790 --> 31:44.520
I fear Young Lord Xiao
may have ulterior motives.

31:46.400 --> 31:47.200
Pass my order:

31:47.790 --> 31:48.750
Act as usual.

31:49.270 --> 31:50.270
Lure the enemy in!

31:50.400 --> 31:51.060
Roger that!

31:52.960 --> 31:55.420
It seems Your Highness
has never trusted me.

31:56.110 --> 31:58.060
Was my acting really that bad?

31:58.550 --> 32:00.440
Your acting was excellent,
Young Lord Xiao.

32:00.440 --> 32:02.350
It's just a pity I don't care for plays.

32:02.350 --> 32:04.960
If you told me you were
plotting a rebellion, I'd believe it.

32:04.960 --> 32:06.720
But that you'd defect to Northern Qin?

32:06.720 --> 32:08.440
No matter how well your acting was,

32:08.440 --> 32:09.640
I'd never believe it.

32:14.750 --> 32:16.080
My men have all arrived.

32:16.550 --> 32:17.410
Today is the day

32:17.920 --> 32:19.390
that Beifu meets its end!

32:41.680 --> 32:42.830
They are all still alive?

32:42.830 --> 32:44.110
Even if the Xiao family were to die,

32:44.110 --> 32:46.110
they'd only die on the battlefield.

32:46.110 --> 32:48.110
How could they possibly die because of
your schemes and treachery?

32:48.110 --> 32:51.200
So it was all fake
from the very beginning?

32:52.030 --> 32:53.160
Warriors of Beifu!

32:54.590 --> 32:59.720
Charge!

32:59.720 --> 33:03.510
Kill!

33:10.640 --> 33:11.800
Wuyi, catch this!

33:19.880 --> 33:21.200
Move, move. Faster.

33:21.920 --> 33:22.630
Faster!

33:23.030 --> 33:23.440
Move.

33:24.400 --> 33:24.950
Hurry up!

33:25.680 --> 33:26.270
Hurry!

33:29.870 --> 33:30.600
Move faster!

33:31.030 --> 33:31.550
Come on!

33:33.830 --> 33:34.480
Faster!

33:34.750 --> 33:36.210
What are you dawdling for?

33:51.440 --> 33:52.110
Promise me

33:54.200 --> 33:56.060
you'll take good care of yourself

33:58.750 --> 34:00.280
and wait for me to come back.

34:01.110 --> 34:02.000
Xiao Wuyi.

34:02.200 --> 34:03.000
You liar!

34:03.550 --> 34:04.350
Move, move.

34:07.510 --> 34:08.230
Faster!

34:09.110 --> 34:10.000
Move faster!

34:12.070 --> 34:12.510
Move.

34:15.480 --> 34:16.070
Grandma!

34:16.120 --> 34:16.760
What are you doing?

34:16.760 --> 34:17.360
Hurry up.

34:18.070 --> 34:19.130
What are you doing?

34:19.880 --> 34:20.590
Stop hitting him!

34:20.590 --> 34:21.190
Get up!

34:29.360 --> 34:30.110
My kid...

34:30.110 --> 34:31.960
What are you looking at? Get to work!

34:31.960 --> 34:34.000
Killing is for the sake of saving lives.

34:34.000 --> 34:34.760
Xie Jiayu.

34:35.510 --> 34:37.170
You're not left with nothing.

34:48.810 --> 34:50.630
The Northern Qin people see us Ye people
as nothing more than pigs and sheep

34:50.630 --> 34:51.960
to be slaughtered.
Rather than waiting here to die

34:51.960 --> 34:53.000
and be slaughtered,

34:53.000 --> 34:54.530
why not take up your weapons

34:54.800 --> 34:55.659
and fight them?

34:58.880 --> 35:00.030
They are no different from us.

35:00.030 --> 35:01.230
They are also made of flesh and blood.

35:01.230 --> 35:02.960
They too will die and feel fear.

35:20.760 --> 35:21.440
Don't you

35:22.070 --> 35:24.630
want to go home?

35:27.270 --> 35:29.000
We all will die sooner or later.

35:29.000 --> 35:30.460
At worst, we die together!

35:31.920 --> 35:33.230
No one is born a coward.

35:33.920 --> 35:36.320
It's just when they become accustomed to
bowing their heads,

35:36.320 --> 35:37.850
courage and determination

35:38.110 --> 35:39.910
must be shown to them by someone—

35:39.960 --> 35:41.480
with their life and blood.

35:52.400 --> 35:53.600
You came just in time.

35:53.630 --> 35:54.550
Let's get this over with quickly

35:54.550 --> 35:55.510
and go save Xiao Wuyi.

35:55.510 --> 35:58.110
He's about to take the Eagle King
down with him.

36:29.250 --> 36:29.770
Father.

36:34.800 --> 36:36.550
Xiao Wuyi, you've lost.

36:38.000 --> 36:39.260
Today, Dingfeng Slope

36:39.710 --> 36:41.760
will be the graveyard
for both you and the Beifu Army!

36:41.760 --> 36:43.020
Who wins and who loses,

36:43.670 --> 36:45.030
who lives and who dies—

36:45.920 --> 36:47.450
it still remains to be seen.

36:55.590 --> 36:57.390
His Majesty's army has arrived!

37:14.400 --> 37:14.920
Defend!

37:29.250 --> 37:29.780
Retreat!

37:36.920 --> 37:37.550
Attack!

37:37.800 --> 37:38.440
Attack!

37:38.630 --> 37:39.510
Attack!

37:39.510 --> 37:41.360
Attack!

37:53.070 --> 37:53.760
Eagle King.

37:54.270 --> 37:55.530
How could you run away?

37:56.070 --> 37:57.760
This battle has just begun.

37:59.000 --> 38:00.480
So you threw yourself into this

38:00.480 --> 38:01.440
not for me,

38:01.920 --> 38:02.520
but for...

38:02.800 --> 38:05.440
Think about it. Prince Qi wouldn't let me
take all the military credit.

38:05.440 --> 38:06.280
Then would your young emperor

38:06.280 --> 38:08.280
spare a powerful minister like you?

38:08.920 --> 38:10.590
Now that we've both suffered heavy losses,

38:10.590 --> 38:12.120
he wants to reap the spoils.

38:12.360 --> 38:13.480
But little does he know

38:13.480 --> 38:15.480
that he's the real prey in this game.

38:45.110 --> 38:45.710
Load!

38:48.480 --> 38:49.110
Prime!

38:53.760 --> 38:54.480
Fire!

39:17.960 --> 39:21.000
So this is the true main force
of the Beifu Army.

39:21.320 --> 39:22.100
The Beifu Army

39:22.100 --> 39:24.550
has burned and cut off
all the escape routes from Dingfeng Slope!

39:24.550 --> 39:27.840
Xiao Wuyi saw that I was at odds with
His Majesty,

39:28.880 --> 39:30.150
so he deliberately put himself
into this fray,

39:30.150 --> 39:31.920
all to lure His Majesty into taking action
so he could wipe out the main force

39:31.920 --> 39:34.670
of our Northern Qin Army
here at Dingfeng Slope.

39:35.670 --> 39:36.760
He and his father

39:37.310 --> 39:39.110
never intended to return alive.

39:42.230 --> 39:43.550
Even if I die today,

39:44.320 --> 39:46.120
I'll personally finish you off!

39:58.590 --> 39:59.110
Yao!

40:41.670 --> 40:44.000
Father!

40:52.860 --> 40:53.510
Father...

41:05.760 --> 41:06.400
Father...

41:23.710 --> 41:26.280
Father!

41:44.390 --> 41:45.790
-Father!
-Yao, let's go!

41:46.440 --> 41:47.240
I won't leave.

42:04.840 --> 42:05.770
Don't look back.

42:06.010 --> 42:06.570
Go!

42:06.630 --> 42:07.280
Father!

42:17.190 --> 42:19.440
Wuyi, I can agree to your plan,

42:19.800 --> 42:21.310
but you need to agree to one condition:

42:21.310 --> 42:22.440
you must stay alive.

42:23.190 --> 42:24.630
Those with ambition cling to life;

42:24.630 --> 42:26.630
those who die for their cause seek death.

42:26.630 --> 42:28.960
Xiao Wuyi, cling to life for me
from now on,

42:29.670 --> 42:30.280
will you?

42:31.230 --> 42:32.510
I'm sorry, Yaoyao.

43:10.920 --> 43:11.670
Fire!

43:18.360 --> 43:18.960
Xiao Wuyi!

43:19.320 --> 43:20.050
You lunatic!

43:20.480 --> 43:21.710
As Crown Prince Wenxi,

43:21.710 --> 43:23.440
do you really have no regard
for your own life?

43:23.440 --> 43:24.370
Someone like you

43:25.030 --> 43:27.230
will never understand
what I've been fighting for in this life.
